	m. The Zoom link will be the same for every meeting and will be provided i
	n your Eventbrite email receipt (scroll down to the Additional Information
	 section). \n  \n \nOn June 30\, 2026 the Inprint BCM HEAL Book Club will 
	discuss Can’t We Talk About Something More Pleasant?: A Memoir by Roz Chas
	t. \nInprint BCM HEAL Book Club meetings are free and designed for those i
	nvolved in the healthcare community. Meetings are facilitated by Stacy Nig
	liazzo. The full schedule of Inprint BCM HEAL Book Club meetings for 2026 
